The new autumn/winter 2019 collection is here

Find your nearest store and discover our new products >>>

   The new autumn/winter collection is here!
   you’ll find innovative products like the “It series” warming gloves
   with original integrated technology,
   as well as a range of urban/heritage jackets, shoes and gloves
   … not forgetting the new roadster-inspired products with ixon dna.

CHOOSE YOUR STYLE

OUR INNOVATIONS

   Ixon’s R&D works tirelessly to offer the most technical and innovative
   new products every year.
   in 2019 we’re celebrating the sale of the IX-Airbag-uo3 (inemotion
   technology)
   and the arrival of the it series warming gloves (Clim8 technology).

OUR RIDERS

   Competition: a well-known and famousdna
   that ixon strives to maintain and improve on, to achieve a solid
   international
   reputation for the brand.

FOLLOW 2019 SEASON

   GP, Moto2, MotoE, Superbike, Supersport, Endurance, Supermotard…
   these are the flagship Disciplines where Ixon has a strong presence
   sponsoring elite competitors.
   READ MORE

OUR KNOW-HOW

   We endeavour to accompany each of our drivers for the whole season.
   Our Ix-Lab (custom suit manufacturing) and Innovating Racing Lab
   (mobile unit present at gp) departments are dedicated soleley to
   competitive racing.

UNIQUE KNOW-HOW

   Ix-Lab, the Ixon Racing Equipment department, hand crafts suits for our
   international drivers. from taking measurements to the first time out
   on the track, Ix-lab goes the extra mile to offer each driver perfectly
   tailored suits.
   READ MORE

INNOVATIVE RACING LAB

   Innovating Racing Lab is the Ixon mobile unit that monitors drivers at
   each Grand Prix. it’s the lead department at races, which allows it to
   offer services and advice specific to the drivers.
   READ MORE

IXON_OFFICIAL

   No matter what you ride or how you ride,
   stay connected, share your experience and your passion with Ixon
   #RIDEYOURWAY
   IXON_INSTAGRAM

